<l>tūṅkuka tūṅkic ceyaṟpāla tūṅkaṟka </l>
<l>tūṅkātu ceyyum viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sleep over such (actions) as may be slept over (but) never over such as may not be slept over</l>
